 | author2 =Kalus Hornberger
 | title =Testing the limits of quantum superpositions
 | journal =Nature Physics
 | volume =10
 | pages =271-277
 | date =2014
 | url =https://arxiv.org/abs/1410.0270
 | doi =10.1038/nphys2863
 | quote =Quantum mechanics has passed all precision tests with flying colours.
 | author =
 | access-date =2016-10-06
 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20161009102542/https://arxiv.org/abs/1410.0270
 | archive-date =2016-10-09
 | dead-url =no
 }}</ref>

[[量子場論|量子場論]]統一了量子力學和狹義相對論，是[[粒子物理學|粒子物理學]]不可或缺的基礎理論。<ref name=Griffiths2008/>{{rp|2}}[[電磁交互作用|電磁交互作用]]與[[弱交互作用|弱交互作用]]也已被合併為[[電弱交互作用|電弱交互作用]]。<ref name=Griffiths2008/>{{rp|338-346}}物理學者期望在不久的未來，[[電磁交互作用|電磁交互作用]]、[[強交互作用|強交互作用]]與[[弱交互作用|弱交互作用]]能夠被收斂在[[大一統理論|大一統理論]]的論述內。<ref name=Griffiths2008/>{{rp|84-85}}[[廣義相對論|廣義相對論]]將時空延伸為動態的彎曲時空，能夠描述大質量系統和[[宇宙|宇宙]]的大尺寸結構。<ref name=TiplerLlewellyn2003/>{{Rp|3-4}}但是，廣義相對論與其它種基礎相互作用表述尚未能被統一為單一理論；科學家仍舊在發展幾種可能的[[量子引力|量子引力]]理論。<ref name="#1">{{Cite web|title = Quantum gravity - Scholarpedia|url = http://www.scholarpedia.org/article/Quantum_gravity|website = www.scholarpedia.org|accessdate = 2016-01-09|last = Rovelli|first = Carlo|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180704003925/http://www.scholarpedia.org/article/Quantum_gravity|archive-date = 2018-07-04|dead-url = no}}</ref>

